document_data.History:
Groshin was tortured by [[Thayan]]s as a young man.

In time, he became the leader of the Hawks in Mulmaster, one of the most trusted servants of High Blade [[Jaseen Drakehorn]]. He also had dealings with the [[Lords' Alliance]].

In 1491 DR, he hired an adventuring party to discover what had happened to a nearby iron mine, after a previous expedition of soldiers had disappeared.{{Cite adventurers league/Mayhem in the Earthspur Mines|6-7}}
